like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"越南屋"},{"pid":"9eaf40ac2a3021b690c421007e63e5a09618fd3c","tid":2129510,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"多謝巴絲推介<br />\n逐間試先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5329a1639836ab3213e54732308f904394209287","tid":2129510,"uid":181549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:31:59.000Z","msg":"LLB Bistro<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下叫春文：<br />\n要黎嘅始終都要黎<br />\n全日禁堂食今日29/7開始<br />\n究竟LLB應該要點樣先可以係呢段時間生存落去？<br />\n19年1月開舖人流極少，個個月赤字捱到6月諗住會慢慢變好；<br />\n19年6月反送中運動，參於罷市生意一落千丈，個個月都六位數字蝕到去10月；<br />\n黃藍地圖出現救左LLB，以為搵到生存空間，直到武漢肺炎出現......<br />\n創業，捱過；<br />\n社運，捱過；<br />\n疫情初期，捱過；<br />\n限聚令，都捱過；<br />\n禁堂食，一間西餐廳點捱？<br />\n<br />\n政府唔封關，我哋只可以繼續硬食。<br />\n<br />\n以下為營業時間：<br />\n12-3pm<br />\nLunch menu 外賣自取八折<br />\n<br />\n3-9pm<br />\nTakeaway menu &amp; Snack Menu 外賣自取八折<br />\n<br />\n6-9pm<br />\nA-La-Carte menu 外賣自取八折<br />\n<br />\n以上menu可以睇Story Highlight🙏🏻<br />\n想送到府上請用Foodpanda/Uber Eats<br />\n<br />\n另外有唔同平台都準備緊，希望可以盡快推出自救😢<br />\n<br />\n冇瞓過教嘅腦細 @llbbistrohk <br />\n<br />\n#封關救港 #林鄭死全家 #黃店 #良心小店 #外賣自取 #上環美食 #上環黃店"},{"pid":"e09d58780be2e3b3aa824dc6277c7f9bc41398d0","tid":2129510,"uid":94454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:37:47.000Z","msg":"永樂餃子店"},{"pid":"31295cc5cd264a1ddd2e0a3ffd0d40bd75a7391e","tid":2129510,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/98/%E5%A4%8F%E9%9B%A8%EF%B8%B0%E5%8A%89%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%80%E8%BA%AB%E8%9F%BB.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/340?cb=20100407045608\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F98%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E9%259B%25A8%25EF%25B8%25B0%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8